Type: Package
Package: segmentr
Title: Tools for Customer Segmentation Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Aravind", "Hebbali", email = "hebbali.aravind@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for segmentation of customers using RFM (recency, frequency and monetary) analysis. Generate RFM score,
    heatmap for average monetary value for different recency and frequency scores, histograms of scores, examine the distribution
    of monetary score for the different combinations of frequency and recency scores, scatter plots for examining the relationship
    between the scores.
